  <title>Creating a Blog Post</title>
  <dc:creator>Caleb Grant</dc:creator>
  <link>http://toolkit.goecoug.com/docs/blog/posts/creating-a-post/index.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p>To add a post, create a copy of <code>docs/blog/posts/_template</code>, modify the folder name with the title of the post, then update the <code>index.qmd</code> with your content. New posts under <code>docs/blog/posts</code> will show up in the <a href="../../../../docs/blog/index.html">blog listings</a> when the site is rendered.</p>



